## Post 2

**Date:** 2nd July, 2026

**Topic:** Career setbacks can become turning points

### Summary
Dave reflects on being rejected for a job roughly ten years ago. While disappointing at the time, he now considers it one of the best things that happened to his career and shares the story to encourage others facing similar setbacks.

### Main Takeaway
