## Post 5

**Date:** 1st july, 2026

**Topic:** Offline (IRL) marketing still matters

### Summary
Dave shares an example of Exit Five investing in physical advertising through sponsorship placements at New England PGA golf courses in Vermont. He contrasts this with spending exclusively on digital advertising like Google Ads and highlights the importance of experimenting with real-world brand visibility.

### Main Takeaway
Not all marketing needs to happen online. Strategic offline experiences can strengthen brand awareness and create memorable customer interactions that digital advertising alone may not achieve.

